videos.headline: Ball State QB hurt in first career start
videos.description: Cardinals' quarterback Zack Blair hurts his ankle on a sack and has to exit the game. He is the third quarterback to start for Ball State this season.

videos.headline: Cardinals' Dunner runs 41 yards for TD
videos.description: Ball State's Malik Dunner finds the hole and runs up the middle for a touchdown from 41 yards out

videos.headline: Ball State's Winbush gets injured on play
videos.description: Cardinals DE Anthony Winbush is carried off the field with apparent ankle injury. Winbush is second in the country in sacks.

videos.headline: Toledo's Swanson runs 71 yards for TD
videos.description: Rockets' Terry Swanson avoids a tackle, finds a gap, and runs for a 71-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Rockets' Woodside finds Phillips for TD
videos.description: Toledo's Logan Woodside finds Desmond Phillips for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Cardinals' Hall hurdles over Toldeo player
videos.description: Ball State's Drew Plitt finds Justin Hall, who hurdles over a Toledo player for a first down.

videos.headline: Toledo extends lead with a 67-yard TD
videos.description: Rockets' Logan Woodside finds Diontae Johnson for a 67-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Toledo's Johnson gets second TD of game
videos.description: Logan Woodside finds Diontae Johnson, who bobbles the catch then runs the ball in for an 88-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Great TD run by Rockets' Seymour
videos.description: Shakif Seymour is handed off the ball, and dodges multiple tackles for a 63-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Great 73-yard run by Toledo's McCrimmon
videos.description: Rockets' Nevone McCrimmon runs for 73-yards for a first down, and avoids multiple tackles.
